-- Innova disc_molds seed (Track 1B) — 17 popular Innova Champion Discs molds,
-- live-scraped 2026-07-04 from https://www.innovadiscs.com/disc/<mold>/ (flight
-- numbers, category, the manufacturer's prose description, and the manufacturer's
-- own image URL — referenced for attribution, never downloaded).
--
-- Requires disc_molds (disc_locker_and_layouts_schema.sql) + the enrichment
-- columns (disc_molds_enrichment.sql: description, source_url) + the provenance
-- columns (disc_molds_provenance.sql: source_name, scraped_at). See CLAUDE.md
-- "Seeding disc catalog data". Idempotent: ON CONFLICT on the case-insensitive
-- (manufacturer, mold_name) unique index DO NOTHING.
--
-- Descriptions use dollar-quoting ($d$...$d$) so apostrophes need no escaping.

on conflict (lower(manufacturer), lower(mold_name)) do nothing;
